io.github.msdk.datamodel

Interface MsSpectrum

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    MsScan
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMsSpectrum, MgfMsSpectrum, MspSpectrum, MzMLMsScan, NetCDFMsScan, PeakInvestigatorMsSpectrum, SimpleMsScan, SimpleMsSpectrum

    public interface MsSpectrum
    A mass spectrum. This is a base interface typically extended by other, more specialized interfaces. It may represent a single scan in raw MS data, a calculated isotope pattern, a predicted fragmentation spectrum of a molecule, etc.

      • getSpectrumType

        @Nonnull
MsSpectrumType getSpectrumType()
        Returns the type of this mass spectrum. For spectra that are loaded from raw data files, the type is detected automatically. For calculated spectra, the type depends on the method of calculation.
        Returns:
        spectrum type (profile, centroided, thresholded)
